query:
SELECT wl.id, wl.code, wl.tenantId, t.name as tenantName, wl.status 
FROM warehouseLocations wl 
LEFT JOIN tenants t ON wl.tenantId = t.id 
WHERE wl.code LIKE '%REC%';
